-- aditi.h2: QUOTES

Quote is something that helps you to give motivation in life.





-- aditi.code: Code for  `-- Quote-1`
lang: ftd

\-- whitey1: Lebbeus Woods
label: Software Developer

Architecture is about ideas
in the first place. You don't
get to design until you
have an idea.





-- whitey1: Lebbeus Woods
label: Software Developer

Architecture is about ideas
in the first place. You don't
get to design until you
have an idea.










